elated to this plan was approximately $76,000 during the ten months ended November 1, 2002, and $119,000 and $174,000 for the years ended December 31, 2001 and 2000, respectively. InNet sponsors a SIMPLE IRA plan for its employees. InNet's contributions to this plan on behalf of its employees were $36,000 during the ten months ended November 1, 2002 and $37,000 for the year ended December 31, 2001. - 18 -
