No Consents
. Except as set forth on
Schedule 2.4
, no consent, notice, approval, waiver, license or other authorization or action by or filing, registration or qualification with any Governmental Entity or any other Person (including any party to any agreement with the Company) is required in connection with the execution and delivery by the Company of this Agreement, the consummation by the Company of the transactions contemplated hereby, or the performance by the Company of its obligations hereunder.
 
Section 2.5.
 
