also contains a complete list of all machinery, motor vehicles, computer equipment, other equipment, furniture, fixtures, and all other tangible personal property (i) owned by the Company and used in connection with the Business on the date hereof and (ii) leased by the Company and used in connection with the Business on the date hereof pursuant to leases which involve monthly payments of more than $500 per month on account of any such lease. Neither the Company nor, to the Companys Knowledge, any lessor of any such lease is in default under any such lease and, to the Companys Knowledge, no facts exists which, with notice and/or the passage of time, would constitute such a default.
 
