(b)
 
a number equal to 1.00
minus
the aggregate of the then stated maximum rates during such Interest Period of all reserve requirements (including marginal, emergency, supplemental and special reserves), expressed as a decimal, established by the Board of Governors and any other banking authority to which BNY and other major money center banks chartered under the laws of the United States or any State thereof are subject, in respect of eurocurrency funding (currently referred to as
eurocurrency liabilities
