Excluded Subsidiaries
 means, collectively, (i) Bel Delaware LLC, a Delaware limited liability company and a Wholly Owned Subsidiary of the Hong Kong Subsidiary, and (ii) each of Transformer One LLC, Transformer Two LLC, Transformer Three LLC, Transformer Four LLC, Transformer Five LLC and Transformer Six LLC (each, a 
