On May 3, 2011, Bel Fuse Inc. (the Company) announced via press release that it has mailed a letter to the shareholders of Pulse Electronics Corporation (Pulse) in connection with Pulses 2011 annual meeting of shareholders scheduled for May 18, 2011.  The press release and letter to shareholders of Pulse have been posted to www.ProxyProcess.com/BelFuse.
 
A copy of the press release is attached as Exhibit 99.1 hereto and incorporated herein by reference. A copy of the letter to shareholders of Pulse is attached as Exhibit 99.2 hereto and incorporated herein by reference.
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
Pursuant to the requirements of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, the registrant has duly caused this report to be signed on its behalf by the undersigned hereunto duly authorized.
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 

