JERSEY CITY, N.J.-- today announced that it has issued a shareholder presentation and mailed a letter to the shareholders of Pulse Electronics Corporation (NYSE: - ) in connection with Pulse's 2011 annual meeting of shareholders scheduled for May 18, 2011.
