(c)
 
With respect to the third party Contracts and third party purchase orders under which Purchaser has Assumed Liabilities pursuant to Section 2.4(c), Purchaser agrees to cooperate with Seller in endeavoring to obtain for Seller or its applicable Affiliate, at no cost to Purchaser, the Seller Entities, the Conveyed Companies or any of their respective Affiliates or Subsidiaries, an arrangement whereby Seller, or its applicable Affiliate, is released by the relevant Person under each Contract or purchase order from all Liabilities which constitute Assumed Liabilities.  For the avoidance of doubt, the failure to obtain any release or consent pursuant to this Section 2.6 shall not relieve Purchaser of any of its obligations with respect to the Assumed Liabilities.
 
