not agree to do anything (A) prohibited by this Section 5.2, or (B) intended to make any of the representations and warranties of Seller in this Agreement or any of the Ancillary Agreements or instruments or documents delivered in connection herewith or therewith untrue or incorrect in any material respect.
 
