the sole and exclusive remedy of any Seller Indemnitee with respect to any and all Losses arising in connection with the representations, warranties and covenants set forth in this Agreement shall be pursuant to the indemnification obligations set forth in Section 7.6 and Section 8.3.
 
 
 
 
