:  This Amendment No. 1 amends the Current Report on Form 8-K filed on April 4, 2013 by Bel Fuse Inc. (the Company) to update the financial statements and pro forma financial information required to be filed under Item 9.01 related to the Companys acquisition of the Transpower magnetics business of TE Connectivity on March 29, 2013.
Explanatory Note
 
 
Item 9.01.   Financial Statements and Exhibits.
 
The Registrant has determined that pursuant to Rule 3-05(b)(2) of Regulation S-X, no financial statements of the acquired business are required to be filed.
The Registrant has determined that pursuant to Article 11 of Regulation S-X, no pro forma financial information related to the acquired business is required to be filed
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
Pursuant to the requirements of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, the registrant has duly caused this report to be signed on its behalf by the undersigned thereunto duly authorized.
 


</DOCUMENT>
